#   4. Copy the key below (looks like AIzaSy...)
#
# Then run the Flask service:
#   Windows:  set GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSy...  && python app.py
#   Linux/Mac: GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSy... python app.py

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
